# IMPLEMENTATION ORDER

## Phase 1: Creative Review Hub (Ad Campaign Engine) — PRIORITY
1. Add 3 new Convex tables (creativeReviews, reviewActivity, reviewSettings)
2. Modify creatives table (add reviewStatus, lastReviewId)
3. Build backend module (creativeReviews.ts — all 13 functions)
4. Build AI pre-scoring action (creativeReviewActions.ts)
5. Build ReviewHubPage.tsx with all 5 sections
6. Build ReviewModal component (single creative review)
7. Build BatchReview component 
8. Build BeforeAfterView component
9. Add sidebar nav item with pending badge
10. Wire routing in App.tsx

## Phase 2: Konstant Landing Templates (Offer Engine) — PRIORITY
1. Create 5 section template components
2. Create seed data for sectionTemplates table
3. Create 2 full page template seeds
4. Register components in funnel builder section picker
5. Add "Konstant Collection" filter to TemplatesPage
6. Add konstant color tokens to Tailwind config
7. Test all 5 sections in responsive views
8. Test full page template assembly in funnel builder

## TESTING CHECKLIST
- [ ] Review queue loads with pending creatives
- [ ] Single review modal scores and saves correctly
- [ ] Approve → creative status changes to "ready"
- [ ] Reject → creative stays "draft" with feedback
- [ ] Batch review approves/rejects multiple
- [ ] Auto-approve triggers for score >= 90
- [ ] Before/After view renders correctly
- [ ] All 5 section templates render on desktop + mobile
- [ ] Anchor pricing calculates savings correctly
- [ ] Hero carousel scrolls/snaps properly
- [ ] Transformation carousel navigates
- [ ] Dark CTA gradient renders correctly
- [ ] Templates appear in TemplatesPage
- [ ] Sections available in FunnelBuilderPage
- [ ] Brand color override works
- [ ] No console errors, no infinite re-renders
